---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | ACHV Ltd."
  description="Privacy Policy for ACHV Ltd., a Malta-based project management, construction and finishes company."
>
  <section class="px-6 py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 leading-8 text-black/70">
        <p>ACHV Ltd. respects your privacy and processes personal data responsibly.</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black">Information we collect</h2>
        <p>When you use the contact form, we may collect your name, email address, phone number, project location, project type, project stage and message. We may also collect any information you send through direct communication channels.</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black">How we use your information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to respond to enquiries, assess project requirements, provide services and maintain business communication.</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black">Lawful basis</h2>
        <p>We process contact form submissions on the basis of your consent and our legitimate interest in responding to business enquiries and managing potential project relationships.</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black">Form processing provider</h2>
        <p>ACHV uses Web3Forms as the form-processing provider for website enquiries. Form submissions are sent securely over HTTPS and forwarded to ACHV so we can respond.</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black">Data sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell personal data. We only use service providers where needed to operate the website, process enquiries or maintain business communication.</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black">Your rights</h2>
        <p>You can request access, correction or deletion of your personal data by emailing hello@achv.today.</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black">Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy-related requests, contact hello@achv.today.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
